 content[14] = '<p>"Thank you very much for sharing this web site with the world and being an excellent teacher so far. I love and enjoy studying Japanese on your site almost every day since this new year when I found the site. I hope to take JLPT some day and master the Japanese language like you did. I have reverence for your study of the Japanese language."<br><br>- Kim Morimoto, New Zealand</p>';
